def categorical_coded(col, dict):
    col = pd.Series(col, copy = True)
    
    for key, value in dict.items():
        col.replace(key, value, inplace = True)
    
    return col

df_loan['loan_status_cate'] = categorical_coded(df.loan_status, 
                                                {
                                                    'Current': 0,
                                                    'Fully Paid': 0,
                                                    'In Grace Period': 1,
                                                    'Late (31-120 days)': 1,
                                                    'Late (16-30 days)': 1,
